#Here we provide a demo dataset with KO abundance of 622 paired WGS-amplicon microbiomes
#
#File description
#training.wgs.ko.abd: the gene relative abundance table of 15 training WGS samples.
#training.16s.ko.abd: the gene relative abundance table of 15 matched training amplicon samples.
#16s.KO.abd: the gene profiles of samples for calibration.
#meta.txt: the meta-data of samples for calibration.
#To run the demo, you can either
#
#sh Readme
#
#or
#type the following command
#
#Commands
meta-apo-train -T training.wgs.ko.abd -t training.16s.ko.abd -o meta-apo.model
##Calibration step
meta-apo-calibrate -t 16s.ko.abd -m meta-apo.model -o 16s.ko.calibrated.abd
#Output description
#meta-apo-model.txt: mapping model
#
#meta-apo-calibrated: The calibration file path.
